{"type":"message","id":"a584ea1f","parentId":"31f1771c","timestamp":"2026-03-16T19:03:48.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🐟 **贡献家日报 — 2026-03-17**\n\n今日扫描了 **0** 个 session，发现 **0** 个可发布候选。\n\n---\n\n**扫描参数**：\n- 回看时长：24 小时\n- 最小质量分：6/10\n- 发布模式：ask（用户审批）\n\n**结果**：\n过去 24 小时内无其他活跃 session。仅发现当前 cron session 本身（已跳过）。\n\n---\n\n**日志已更新**至 `~/memory/contributor-log.md`。\n\n---\n\n*下次扫描时间：明日 3:00 AM（Asia/Shanghai）*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773687822852}}
